<p>Dave and John kick off the week helping you prep for Mac OS X Lion, discussing a few tips that will pave the way for your migration to Apple&rsquo;s 10.7 version of their desktop operating system. Then it&rsquo;s off to the races with tons of question and answers about all things Mac and Apple, with topics including System Profiler crashes, displaying non-Apple content on your Apple TV, and a few iTunes questions, too. Download today &mdash; it&rsquo;s free &mdash; and enjoy!</p>
